        <ul>
          <li>Clear Lake</li>
          <li>St. Cloud</li>
          <li>Sartell</li>
          <li>Sauk Rapids</li>
          <li>Waite Park</li>
          <li>Cold Spring</li>
          <li>And surrounding communities</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Service availability outside our primary area may be subject to additional travel fees. Please contact us to confirm service availability in your area.
        </p>

