        <p>
          <strong>Scheduling:</strong> Project start dates are scheduled based on mutual agreement. We will make every effort to begin and complete projects according to the agreed timeline, but delays may occur due to weather, material availability, or other unforeseen circumstances.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Cancellation:</strong> If you need to cancel or reschedule a project, please notify us as soon as possible. Cancellations made less than 48 hours before a scheduled start date may be subject to a cancellation fee to cover preparation costs.
        </p>

        <h2>Payment Terms</h2>

        <p>Payment terms will be specified in your project estimate or contract. General terms include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>A deposit may be required to secure scheduling for larger projects</li>
          <li>Progress payments may be required for extended projects</li>
          <li>Final payment is due upon completion and your satisfaction with the work</li>
          <li>We accept cash, checks, and major credit cards</li>
